{
  "stem": "1183.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my mother was actually never conscious when she came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The doctor's office returned my mother on a stretcher to our home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She was put to bed, and we called the doctor again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the doctor told us, sorry Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Mossel, we cannot admit your wife because she's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we don't want the Jewish there in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I'd guess and see now, she had a serious stroke.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was in a coma, and still was on the bed thrashing around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then come quiet, all the bodily functions just went without her knowing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was in a coma from that Friday morning till the Monday night at August 31, 1942 when she died.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the meantime, I didn't-- when my grandmother died, my grandfather came to live with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here we were, the three of us left alone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Devastated, I didn't go to the funeral.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just accompanied the coffin to the end of the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Across the street there lived a fascist family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They never had any decent meals during the whole time when the time was normal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a shoemaker and couldn't make any-- how do you say it in Dutch?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Earn any dry bread, eat never, very poor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I in the beginning-- sometimes I played with her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not during the war, because they showed very definitely that they didn't like us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They lived right across from us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were laughing when I passed with the coffin of my mother and the whole funeral procession.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They laughed about that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, yes at that time, was not much that in the diamond industry anyway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like everybody else, I assume, and I know he did, the people had to make a living.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
